<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238888>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. The holotype (a: ♂ PSUZC-MM. 2014.157) and paratype (b: ♀ PSUZC-MM. 2014.164) of E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. in comparison with M. lyra ♀ PSUZC-MM. 2014.160 (c) from Satun, S. Thailand, and M. spasma ♂ PSUZC-MM. 2014.163 (d) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238888/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238894>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Right upper (on left) and right lower (on right) first molars of a) M. gigas (♂ HZM. 1.20168) from Northern Territory, Australia; b) E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC-MM 2014.157, holotype) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; c) M. lyra (♀ HZM. 11.39934) from from Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India; d) M. spasma (♂ HZM. 5.28163) from Sirsi, Karnataka, India; e) C. cor (♂ HZM. 12.2641) from Kenya; f) L. frons (sex not known, HZM. 26.7791) from Democratic Republic of Congo. Scale = 1 mm; ant, anterior; lab, labial. Drawings by PJJB and PS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238895>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dorsal view of the skulls of a) M. gigas (♂ HZM. 1.20168) from Northern Territory, Australia; b) E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC-MM 2014.157, holotype) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; c) M. lyra (♀ PSUZC-MM. 2014.160) from Satun, S. Thailand; d) M. spasma (♂ PSUZC-MM. 2014.163) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; e) C. cor (♂ HZM. 12.2641) from Kenya; f) L. frons (sex not known, HZM. 26.7791) from Democratic Republic of Congo. Scale = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238896>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. The dorsal (left) and lateral view (right) of the baculum of a) M. gigas * (♂ HZM. 1.20168) from Northern Territory, Australia; b) E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC-MM 2014.157, holotype) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand (note that right prong is partially broken); c) M. lyra * (♂ HZM. 7.32146) from Vietnam; d) M. spasma (♂ HZM. 3.27330) from Sri Lanka; e) C. cor (♂ HZM. 61.31851) from Djibouti; f) L. frons (♂ HZM. 9.9664) from Nigeria. Scale = 1 mm. Drawings by PJJB and PS. *: the bacula of M. gigas and M. lyra comprise two separate bones, the lateral view of M. lyra was not drawn." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238893>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Lateral views of the skulls and mandibles of a) M. gigas (♂ HZM. 1.20168) from Northern Territory, Australia; b) E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC-MM 2014.157, holotype) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; c) M. lyra (♀ PSUZC- MM. 2014.160) from Satun, S. Thailand; d) M. spasma (♂ PSUZC-MM. 2014.163) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; e) C. cor (♂ HZM. 12.2641) from Kenya; f) L. frons (sex not known, HZM. 26.7791) from Democratic Republic of Congo. Scale = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238893/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238892>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Occlusal views of the skulls (left) and mandibles (right) of a) M. gigas (♂ HZM. 1.20168) from Northern Territory, Australia; b) E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC-MM 2014.157, holotype) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; c) M. lyra (♀ PSUZC-MM. 2014.160) from Satun, S. Thailand; d) M. spasma (♂ PSUZC-MM. 2014.163) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand; e) C. cor (♂ HZM. 12.2641) from Kenya; f) L. frons (sex not known, HZM. 26.7791) from Democratic Republic of Congo. Scale = 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238892/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238891>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Left upper (a) and right lower toothrows (b) of the holotype of E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. (♂ PSUZC- MM 2014.157) from Narathiwat, S. Thailand. Scale = 5 mm. Drawings by PS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238897>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Spectrograms (a, b) and power spectrum (c) of the echolocation call of E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov., ♀ PSUZC- MM. 2014.164 (paratype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238897/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Maximum likelihood tree based on mitochondrial COI gene of E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov., M. lyra, M. spasma, C. cor, with some Rhinopoma, Rhinolophus and Hipposideros as the outgroup." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238889>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Type locality of E. thongareeae gen. sp. nov. and the currently known distribution of C. cor (horizontal lines), L. frons (vertical lines), M. lyra (diagonal lines, top left to bottom right), M. spasma (diagonal lines, bottom left to top right) and M. gigas (squares in Australia) based on data in the IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. The type localities of all synonyms are indicated and assigned to their respective species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238889/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

